OL,3,CPope Francis to be discharged from
OL,4,Chospital on Sunday
OL,6,FPope Francis will be released from
OL,7,Fhospital on Sunday, after more than a
OL,8,Fmonth battling a life-threatening case
OL,9,Fof pneumonia in both lungs.
OL,11,FThe 88-year-old pontiff will require
OL,12,Fat least two months of rest and
OL,13,Frehabilitation as he continues his
OL,14,Frecovery back at the Vatican, his
OL,15,Fdoctors said.
OL,17,FFrancis was admitted to Gemelli
OL,18,Fhospital on 14 February after a bout
OL,19,Fof bronchitis worsened. He later
OL,20,Fdeveloped a case of double pneumonia.
