OL,3,CPope Francis to be discharged from
OL,4,Chospital on Sunday
OL,6,FPope Francis' doctors provided their
OL,7,Ffirst in-person update on the
OL,8,Fpontiff's condition in a month, in a
OL,9,Fsign that he has made good and steady
OL,10,Fprogress.
OL,12,FDr Sergio Alfieri, the head of the
OL,13,Fteam taking care of the pontiff, said:
OL,14,F"The Holy Father will be discharged
OL,15,Ffrom tomorrow in stable clinical
OL,16,Fcondition with a prescription to
OL,17,Fpartially continue drug therapy and a
OL,18,Fconvalescence and rest period of at
OL,19,Fleast two months.
