OL,3,CPope Francis to be discharged from
OL,4,Chospital on Sunday
OL,6,FLast week, the pope approved a new
OL,7,Fthree-year reform process for the
OL,8,FCatholic Church, sending a strong
OL,9,Fsignal he intends to remain in the
OL,10,Fpost despite his lengthy stint in
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FReforms on the table include how to
OL,14,Fgive greater roles to women in the
OL,15,FCatholic Church, including ordaining
OL,16,Fthem as deacons, and the greater
OL,17,Finclusion of non-clergy members in
OL,18,Fgovernance and decision making.
